<SYNC Start=1280245><P Class=ENCC>
- Okay, I can't do this.<br>
- What's wrong?
<SYNC Start=1282679><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1282848><P Class=ENCC>
Well, there is no Vikram.<br>
Ross made him up.
<SYNC Start=1286875><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1287052><P Class=ENCC>
Because I..
<SYNC Start=1288519><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1288687><P Class=ENCC>
I really never have been<br>
in a long-term relationship.
<SYNC Start=1291588><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1291757><P Class=ENCC>
I've never lived with a guy. I've never<br>
even celebrated an anniversary.
<SYNC Start=1296285><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1296461><P Class=ENCC>
So..
<SYNC Start=1298258><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1299564><P Class=ENCC>
If that's too weird for you..
<SYNC Start=1302465><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1302668><P Class=ENCC>
and you want to leave,<br>
I understand.
<SYNC Start=1304795><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1304970><P Class=ENCC>
In fact, I'll close my eyes<br>
to make it less awkward.
<SYNC Start=1308406><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1315814><P Class=ENCC>
You kissed me.
<SYNC Start=1317941><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1320619><P Class=ENCC>
