<SYNC Start=1454576><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1454753><P Class=ENCC>
Look, we can do something else.
<SYNC Start=1456948><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1457122><P Class=ENCC>
Do you want me to<br>
get into the tub and.. thrash?
<SYNC Start=1461252><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1463061><P Class=ENCC>
- What's going on?<br>
