<SYNC Start=1466622><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1466798><P Class=ENCC>
I still love you.
<SYNC Start=1468425><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1468600><P Class=ENCC>
- Let me be a part of this.<br>
- Let me be a part of this!
<SYNC Start=1472559><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1473972><P Class=ENCC>
