<SYNC Start=1476167><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1476374><P Class=ENCC>
Angry sharks turn you on!
<SYNC Start=1479104><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1480479><P Class=ENCC>
