<SYNC Start=1505497><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1507005><P Class=ENCC>
You are an amazing wife.
<SYNC Start=1509974><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1510141><P Class=ENCC>
Really, you are amazing. You were<br>
actually gonna do this for me?
<SYNC Start=1513508><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1513678><P Class=ENCC>
Where do you find the strength<br>
and the understanding for that?
<SYNC Start=1517978><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1519217><P Class=ENCC>
I'm very, very drunk right now.
<SYNC Start=1522015><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1528860><P Class=ENCC>
Ordinarily, I would talk to her,<br>
but my confidence is shaken.
<SYNC Start=1532159><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1532330><P Class=ENCC>
Did I sleep with her?<br>
Did I not sleep with her?
<SYNC Start=1534855><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1535834><P Class=ENCC>
Maybe this is a wake-up call. You know,<br>
